		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If your library is under a free software license, then the license itself is proof that &quot;permission has been granted by the author&quot;. For example, anything copied out of Zap Ruder, such as controller and Zapper reading code, is under the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/prep/maintain/html_node/License-Notices-for-Other-Files.html" class="postlink">GNU Permissive License</a>.

		

		</td>
